reviewText: this may not be fulcis best but who cares it is still a fulci film and it is simply amazing many may have seen some scenes reused in cat in the brain good gore desent story and better then a couple other fulcis like sweet house, door to silence and white fang
This is one of Fulci's weaker films. Alas, by the late 1980's Lucio was relegated to making Italian tv movies and those so-called production values show.
